/index.php/Jaqen_H%27ghar\" title=\"Jaqen H&#39;ghar\">Jaqen H'ghar</a>'s new face as described in <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_47\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 47\">Chapter 47 (Arya IX)</a>. The implication is that Jaqen is probably also the Alchemist and a <a href=\"/index.php/Faceless_Men\" title=\"Faceless Men\">Faceless Man</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Feast_for_Crows-Prologue&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: External links\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tor.com/blogs/2014/01/a-read-of-ice-and-fire-a-feast-for-crows-part-1\">A Read of Ice and Fire: A Feast for Crows, Part 1</a>. Analyses and summary of the chapter by Leigh Butler.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403143630\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.080 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.239 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 262/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 1134/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6277/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 673/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 464/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.140/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.29 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  209.917      1 -total\n 98.52%  206.806      1 Template:Infobox_Chapter_AFfC\n 97.99%  205.693      1 Template:Infobox_Chapter\n 97.36%  204.384   